WEBVTT

16:42.360 --> 16:44.520 line:80%
The county office
suddenly requisitioned grain.

16:44.520 --> 16:45.580 line:80%
Not only grain—

16:45.610 --> 16:46.880 line:80%
they want money too.

16:46.880 --> 16:48.550 line:80%
They're levying it per person—

16:48.550 --> 16:50.280 line:80%
four taels each.

16:50.280 --> 16:51.190 line:80%
That much?
